  ('elementary-10ced7e2-moex-00823', 'elementary-10ced7e2', 'elementary-10ced7e2-moex-110-21e891bc', 'sub-elementary-10ced7e2-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列敘述何者屬於公務人員行政中立的內涵？', '["公務人員原則上不得介入黨政紛爭，但如涉及本身權益，則不在限制範疇", "事務官不得加入政黨或其他政治團體，更不得兼任政黨或其他政治團體之職務", "公務人員應依法公正執行職務，不得對任何團體或個人予以差別待遇", "公務人員不得於請假期間，從事政黨或其他政治團體之活動"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a9ea86dba62c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "dfbc0bd4bafe", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "506", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "人事行政大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "人事行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-10ced7e2-moex-00824', 'elementary-10ced7e2', 'elementary-10ced7e2-moex-110-21e891bc', 'sub-elementary-10ced7e2-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依公務員懲戒法規定，休職之懲戒處分，其懲戒處分行使期間為何？', '["十年", "五年", "一年", "未設期間"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a9ea86dba62c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "dfbc0bd4bafe", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "506", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "人事行政大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "人事行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-10ced7e2-moex-00825', 'elementary-10ced7e2', 'elementary-10ced7e2-moex-110-21e891bc', 'sub-elementary-10ced7e2-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '公務員服務法第14條之1規定，公務員於其離職後三年內，不得擔任與其離職前五年內之職務直接相關 之營利事業董事、監察人、經理、執行業務之股東或顧問。本條規定行政學理稱之為何？', '["「走後門」（backdoor）條款", "「利害關係人」（stakeholder）條款", "「界線防守」（boundaryspanning）條款", "「旋轉門」（revolvingdoor）條款"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:48+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a9ea86dba62c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "dfbc0bd4bafe", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "506", "s": "0205", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "人事行政大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "人事行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
